  "question": {
    "text": "<p>Welk type stof wordt in het bloed van de docent aangetoond? En is zijn immuniteit actief of passief?</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-left-color:!important;border-left-style:none;border-top:1px solid !important;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"2\">aangetoonde stof</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-style:solid !important;border-top-width:1px !important;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-top-style:solid !important;border-top-width:1px !important;width:auto;\">immuniteit</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:!important;border-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-color:!important;border-style:none;width:auto;\">A</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">antigenen van de borrelia-bacterie</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-color:!important;border-bottom-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width: